(2, 1, '2016-04-18 12:05:54', '2016-04-18 12:05:54', 'Jaipur is the pink city of india, is a world renowned tourist attraction. People from all over the world visit this city throughout the year. Hotel neelgiri is a budget hotel which provides all services at very reasonable and competitive rates. The motto being, service with quality.\r\n<h1>location</h1>\r\nThe hotel is located in jaipur city at sikar road, opposite vidhyadhar nagar roadways bus depot. It is between alka cinema on the north and khetan hospital on the south.\r\nIt\'s distance from jaipur railway station and main bus stand of jaipur (sindhi camp) is approximately 5 km. It\'s distance from jaipur airport is approximately 15 kms. It is located at 200ft- wide national highway and taxies and buses are easily available day and night for all places of the city.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2016-05-12 16:34:54', '2016-05-12 16:34:54', '', 0, 'http://hotelneelgiri.in/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
